9
00:00:50,790 --> 00:00:52,750
When someone falls into the trap,

10
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:55,540
the emotional connection
ties into a dead knot.

11
00:00:57,390 --> 00:00:58,880
Then I guess the trap

12
00:00:59,750 --> 00:01:01,110
