[The Perfect Suspect]

17
00:02:47,180 --> 00:02:49,870
[Episode 3]

18
00:02:50,150 --> 00:02:51,010
Officer Zheng,

19
00:02:51,590 --> 00:02:53,150
do you really think I'd

20
00:02:53,310 --> 00:02:54,910
get back at someone

21
