it might affect Lyuyun Group's reputation.

37
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:40,280
The first time we met

38
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,079
[Bond]

39
00:03:41,079 --> 00:03:42,540
was at his art exhibition.

40
00:03:46,150 --> 00:03:47,280
After that,

41
00:03:47,710 --> 00:03:50,000
he started pursuing me intensely,

42
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:53,750
