45
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,310
What did he lie to you?

46
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,840
He was already married.

47
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:23,920
For your smile,

48
00:04:24,190 --> 00:04:25,600
we should have a drink.

49
00:04:28,070 --> 00:04:28,870
Sure.

50
00:05:02,870 --> 00:05:03,920
Since then,

51
