I've been trying to
stay away from Yang Youmo.

52
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:10,720
But I didn't expect it
to be exposed so soon.

53
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:13,750
Even Mrs. Zhang misunderstood me.

54
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,720
She thought I seduced her son

55
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,430
and I was the reason

56
00:05:19,430 --> 00:05:21,090
that their family broke down.

57
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,680
Youmo and I didn't talk much.

58
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,970
I heard something happened to him.

59
00:05:37,190 --> 00:05:38,320
We were classmates,

60
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,720
