My grandson is so pretty.

76
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:33,450
Look at grandma, Tong.

77
00:06:34,159 --> 00:06:35,420
Who would have thought

78
00:06:36,510 --> 00:06:38,710
Luo Lijuan would jump off the building?

79
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,240
And Tong...

80
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:56,310
