85
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,850
That girl was just like her mom.

86
00:07:18,830 --> 00:07:19,870
All this started

87
00:07:21,950 --> 00:07:23,120
when Youmo got

88
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,750
involved with that woman.

89
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:31,360
I'm done with this.

90
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:32,620
It's getting messier.

91
