94
00:07:37,870 --> 00:07:39,270
What's the saying again?

95
00:07:40,510 --> 00:07:43,240
Even the best judge
can't settle family matters.

96
00:07:44,510 --> 00:07:45,950
Lucky for Captain Zheng,

97
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,850
he has no family matters at all.

98
00:07:49,430 --> 00:07:51,690
Who would have such a grudge against them

99
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,310
and let them die this way?

100
00:07:54,190 --> 00:07:56,390
Why don't we ask an outsider to help?

101
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:59,510
Sometimes outsiders see things clearly.

102
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,480
Outsiders?

103
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:02,750
Who?

104
