111
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:38,400
Anyway, let me make it clear in advance,

112
00:08:38,909 --> 00:08:40,000
I'll follow orders,

113
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:40,549
-but personally…
-Okay.

114
00:08:40,549 --> 00:08:41,549
Captain Zheng said

115
00:08:41,549 --> 00:08:42,750
he'll follow orders.

116
00:08:43,270 --> 00:08:44,120
We should all

117
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,840
learn from his spirit.

118
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,720
Applause!

119
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:48,770
[Criminal Investigation Division,
Nanying District Sub-Bureau, Xinggang City]

