123
00:09:04,630 --> 00:09:05,750
Give it to Zhong Ning.

124
00:09:05,750 --> 00:09:07,150
Why me?

125
00:09:07,900 --> 00:09:09,150
[Advisor ID]

126
00:09:09,150 --> 00:09:10,790
Follow orders.

127
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:45,590
It's bland.

128
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,120
You don't know me?

129
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:00,960
Uncle!

130
00:10:07,030 --> 00:10:08,550
Uncle, did you really eat?

131
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:09,670
I did.

132
00:10:10,510 --> 00:10:11,240
Here you go.

133
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,140
Thank you.

134
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,790
I bought you a book.

135
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,030
Thank you, Uncle.

136
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:17,960
And stationery in your favorite color.

137
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:19,070
[Chinese Children's Encyclopedia]

138
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,480
Thank you, Uncle.

139
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:26,790
Don't fight.

140
00:10:28,830 --> 00:10:30,960
Even if we do, not in front of you.

141
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:36,200
What are you doing here?

142
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:43,320
Xi,

143
00:10:44,670 --> 00:10:48,140
do you know your dad
is going to be an advisor

144
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,270
in the criminal police team?

145
00:10:49,270 --> 00:10:50,080
Really?

146
00:10:51,270 --> 00:10:52,440
Let me tell you,

147
00:10:52,930 --> 00:10:55,030
if he really becomes an advisor,

148
00:10:55,030 --> 00:10:56,600
he'll be very busy.

149
00:10:57,550 --> 00:10:59,410
He's already busy at the law firm.

150
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:02,270
He won't even have time to eat with you.

151
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:05,000
Then I don't have to cook for him.

152
00:11:06,260 --> 00:11:07,100
Dad,

153
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:10,520
since you're giving up time at the firm,

154
00:11:10,550 --> 00:11:11,550
do you get paid for

155
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:12,960
being an advisor?

156
00:11:13,910 --> 00:11:14,740
Nope.

157
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:15,630
No money.

158
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:17,050
Even no meals included.

159
00:11:18,870 --> 00:11:20,000
Where are you going?

160
00:11:27,870 --> 00:11:29,080
I'll pay you.

161
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:31,840
Go help Tong and Yang Yan.

162
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:33,120
How did you know?

163
00:11:34,150 --> 00:11:36,670
I saw what you wrote on the board.

164
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:38,330
You peeped at my stuff again.

165
00:11:38,330 --> 00:11:39,640
Dad.

166
00:11:40,550 --> 00:11:41,630
Alright, eat.

167
00:11:41,650 --> 00:11:42,980
I don't need your money.

168
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:44,480
Can I ask him instead?

169
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:44,960
Sure.

170
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:46,590
Eat.

171
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:53,980
Have some meat.

172
00:11:54,660 --> 00:11:55,600
[Tong] [Yang Youmo]
[Yang Yan, Missing, Accident]

173
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:57,270
Yang Youmo's missing
stepdaughter, Yang Yan,

174
00:11:57,270 --> 00:11:58,400
is Xi's schoolmate.

175
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:02,440
So that's why you're
interested in Yang Youmo?

176
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:13,120
I've made my position clear to Master.

177
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,600
I'll follow orders,

178
00:12:15,790 --> 00:12:17,520
but personally I'm against it.

179
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:18,930
Here's your advisor ID.

180
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,650
Tell me, Advisor Zhong,

181
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,510
what did you get from

182
00:12:31,510 --> 00:12:32,710
Zhang Qiaoyun today?

183
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:36,460
You wanna know?

184
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,380
Then tell me first,

185
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,730
what's the deal with Zhao Qian?

186
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:44,790
Zhao Qian's statement
is a mix of truth and lies.

187
00:12:44,790 --> 00:12:47,480
Were you and Yang Youmo just friends?

188
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:47,910
Yes.

189
00:12:47,910 --> 00:12:49,600
I had a relationship with Yang Youmo.

190
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,000
He lied to me.

191
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:51,120
He was already married.

192
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:53,200
I know who killed my son.

193
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:55,630
Zhao Qian, you're the murderer!

194
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:57,720
Fang Qinchun's husband is Qian Cheng.

195
00:12:57,720 --> 00:12:58,910
I don't need a divorce.

196
00:12:58,910 --> 00:12:59,750
My husband is dead.

197
00:12:59,750 --> 00:13:01,440
She practically stole my husband's soul.

198
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,080
It was a misunderstanding.

199
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:04,390
I thought Ms. Zhao seduced my husband,

200
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:04,870
but it wasn't like that.

201
00:13:04,870 --> 00:13:05,460
He embezzled money
from Lyuyun Pharmaceuticals.

202
00:13:05,460 --> 00:13:06,480
[Tong died the same day Luo Lijuan committed suicide]
