00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:11,460
Captain Zheng,

204
00:13:11,870 --> 00:13:12,750
let's start.

205
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:15,730
This is Mr. Zhong,

206
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:18,670
an advosor brought in by Director Zhang.

207
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,860
If you need anything, ask him.

208
00:13:24,670 --> 00:13:26,360
You've all met Zhong Ning.

209
00:13:26,510 --> 00:13:28,710
Yang Youmo's case has caused a big stir.

210
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:30,550
We need to solve it quickly.

211
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:33,120
With approval

212
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:34,910
from city authorities,

213
00:13:34,910 --> 00:13:37,110
he'll assist the police investigation

214
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:38,960
as an expert advisor.

215
00:13:39,670 --> 00:13:40,270
Everyone,

216
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:42,360
let's welcome Mr. Zhong.

217
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:51,080
Master,

218
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:53,320
this isn't your home turf.

219
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:55,320
Are you picking a fight?

220
00:13:58,030 --> 00:13:58,910
Zheng Gang,

221
00:13:59,790 --> 00:14:01,670
I'm leaving him in your hands.

222
00:14:03,210 --> 00:14:04,270
Take care, Master.

223
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:11,840
Get to work. Why are you standing there?

224
00:14:37,070 --> 00:14:41,470
The murderer kidnapped Zhao Qian
to threaten Yang Youmo

225
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,910
and tried to kill Zhao Qian later.

226
00:14:51,220 --> 00:14:52,870
Zhao Qian has mysophobia,

227
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:54,110
