228
00:14:54,110 --> 00:14:54,580
[Child's death suspicious]
[Marital rift suspected]

229
00:14:54,670 --> 00:14:55,910
[Zhang Qiaoyun was out of town
when Luo Lijuan committed suicide]

230
00:14:56,540 --> 00:14:57,890
The murderer paid attention
to the sense of ritual.

231
00:14:57,890 --> 00:14:58,740
[News about Yang Youmo's stepdaughter]

232
00:14:58,830 --> 00:14:59,150
[Just say it if you don't want him to hug you.
Why yell? You're making it difficult for me.]

233
00:14:59,150 --> 00:15:00,040
Letting Yang Youmo climb 92 meters

234
00:15:00,040 --> 00:15:00,680
[Follow-up visit to Yang Yan's school]

235
00:15:00,680 --> 00:15:02,090
and speed at 154 km/h—

236
00:15:02,750 --> 00:15:04,010
there must be a reason.

237
00:15:07,630 --> 00:15:09,490
What does these specific numbers

238
00:15:09,630 --> 00:15:11,030
mean exactly?

239
00:15:14,510 --> 00:15:14,950
Before Yang Youmo died,
his whole family was gone.

240
00:15:14,950 --> 00:15:18,170
[Suspicious footprints,
fingerprints at scene -  pending]

241
00:15:18,500 --> 00:15:20,640
[Yang Youmo's fingerprint
information to be collected]

242
00:15:22,140 --> 00:15:24,810
Tong and Yang Yan died by accident.

243
00:15:25,280 --> 00:15:25,790
[Related transfer records
need further visits]

244
00:15:25,790 --> 00:15:27,530
Only Luo Lijuan committed suicide.

245
00:15:27,530 --> 00:15:28,140
[Yang Youmo's studio]

246
00:15:31,150 --> 00:15:34,750
Did Luo Lijuan really commit suicide
because of a relationship?

247
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:39,120
Were Tong and Yang Yan's
deaths really accidents?

248
00:15:42,270 --> 00:15:44,400
I want to check out Yang Youmo's house.

249
00:15:49,870 --> 00:15:51,610
Yang Youmo's son, Tong,

250
00:15:51,750 --> 00:15:53,960
died in this room.

251
00:15:57,600 --> 00:15:58,960
He was suffocated on this bed

252
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:00,230
by accident—

253
00:16:00,870 --> 00:16:01,840
got tangled in a blanket

254
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:03,390
while moving around.

255
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:06,860
This spot was directly
in front of the baby monitor.

256
00:16:07,060 --> 00:16:08,610
So we can conclude that

257
00:16:08,790 --> 00:16:11,430
it happened about 10 minutes

258
00:16:11,450 --> 00:16:12,850
after Luo Lijuan jumped.

259
00:16:21,430 --> 00:16:22,760
This is Yang Yan's room.

260
00:16:29,770 --> 00:16:31,310
She drew all of these.

261
00:16:31,630 --> 00:16:32,890
She was very talented.

262
00:16:35,890 --> 00:16:36,630
Her book

263
00:16:36,630 --> 00:16:39,490
Rainbow of the Little Princess
was even published.

264
00:16:41,550 --> 00:16:43,570
Rainbow of the Little Princess...

265
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,870
Where did Luo Lijuan jump from?

266
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:52,800
Right there—by the captain.

