Wait—

270
00:17:22,480 --> 00:17:23,940
It's the other way around.

271
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:25,920
Height determines speed.

272
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:28,160
Check how tall Yang Youmo's building is.

273
00:17:28,160 --> 00:17:29,000
