That's why

283
00:18:21,270 --> 00:18:23,870
the killer made Yang Youmo
open the car window

284
00:18:24,860 --> 00:18:26,170
at that exact speed—

285
00:18:30,500 --> 00:18:33,030
to torture him by
making him feel like Luo Lijuan

286
00:18:33,030 --> 00:18:34,270
when she jumped.

287
00:18:34,530 --> 00:18:36,860
And pushed Zhao Qian, who has mysophobia,

288
00:18:37,030 --> 00:18:38,550
into a trash pit.

289
00:18:39,440 --> 00:18:40,480
How much

290
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:43,240
grudge must this killer hold?

291
00:18:44,880 --> 00:18:46,410
According to the analysis,

292
00:18:47,510 --> 00:18:49,920
the murderer was avenging Luo Lijuan.

293
00:18:52,550 --> 00:18:53,400
You're right.

294
00:18:55,270 --> 00:18:57,200
Luo Lijuan is the cause of the case.

295
00:18:58,240 --> 00:18:59,300
And the child, too.

296
00:19:05,550 --> 00:19:06,640
Dajun, Keran,

297
00:19:06,750 --> 00:19:08,960
find out where Luo Lijuan used to go

298
00:19:08,990 --> 00:19:10,160
and who she met.

299
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:12,370
This should be a new breakthrough.

300
00:19:21,110 --> 00:19:23,730
Lijuan was looking forward
to the birth of the baby.

301
00:19:23,730 --> 00:19:25,200
She came to every session of

302
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:26,400
our parenting class.

303
00:19:26,550 --> 00:19:27,880
She was very attentive,

304
00:19:28,070 --> 00:19:29,590
even took notes.

305
00:19:29,590 --> 00:19:30,400
Notes?

306
00:19:31,510 --> 00:19:33,750
What kind of notes?

307
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:39,800
Exactly like this notebook.

308
00:19:43,350 --> 00:19:43,960
Keran,

309
00:19:45,110 --> 00:19:46,100
was there a notebook like this

310
00:19:46,100 --> 00:19:46,790
[Mom's Diary]

311
00:19:46,790 --> 00:19:48,200
in Luo Lijuan's case file?

312
00:19:48,200 --> 00:19:48,790
No.

313
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:51,350
How did you know?

314
00:19:51,510 --> 00:19:52,590
Because I read through

315
00:19:52,590 --> 00:19:54,650
all of Luo Lijuan's files last night.

316
00:19:59,140 --> 00:20:01,150
When did Luo Lijuan's

317
00:20:01,880 --> 00:20:03,720
mental state start to change?

318
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:04,800
I don't know.

319
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:06,750
After giving birth to Tong,

320
00:20:06,750 --> 00:20:08,070
she hadn't come to me

321
00:20:08,070 --> 00:20:09,400
for a long time.

322
00:20:09,770 --> 00:20:12,110
But one time she was very strange.

323
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:14,510
She came from outside and told me

324
00:20:14,790 --> 00:20:16,320
someone was following her.

325
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:20,550
What's wrong?

326
00:20:21,460 --> 00:20:22,860
Someone is following me.

327
00:20:24,070 --> 00:20:25,000
Don't be afraid.

328
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:26,680
[Feihe for Smart Babies]

329
00:20:26,680 --> 00:20:28,750
She seemed off.

330
00:20:28,830 --> 00:20:31,160
I thought she had postpartum depression.

331
00:20:31,270 --> 00:20:32,510
In serious cases,

332
00:20:32,510 --> 00:20:34,370
it can lead to suicidal thoughts.

333
00:20:34,790 --> 00:20:37,200
So I told her to see a doctor.

334
00:20:42,750 --> 00:20:43,480
No.

335
00:20:43,480 --> 00:20:45,840
I even checked
the next store's security footage.

336
00:20:45,840 --> 00:20:48,110
I didn't find anyone following her.

337
00:20:48,350 --> 00:20:50,720
How was Luo Lijuan's
relationship with Yang Youmo?

338
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:52,000
Well,

339
00:20:52,350 --> 00:20:54,240
it's between husband and wife.

340
00:20:54,510 --> 00:20:56,750
It's hard to judge as an outsider.

341
00:20:56,860 --> 00:20:58,070
I can only say

342
00:20:58,440 --> 00:21:00,370
Lijuan loved Yang Youmo very much.

343
00:21:00,390 --> 00:21:04,070
As for Yang Youmo, probably not so much.

344
00:21:04,750 --> 00:21:07,310
At least not the way it looked to others.

345
00:21:07,660 --> 00:21:08,480
But

346
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:10,350
that's just my intuition

347
00:21:10,350 --> 00:21:11,240
as a woman.

348
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,350
What song is this?

349
00:21:19,510 --> 00:21:20,550
Hide and Seek.

350
00:21:21,460 --> 00:21:21,550
♪ A cat sits under the window sill ♪

351
00:21:21,550 --> 00:21:22,110
Oh right,

352
00:21:22,400 --> 00:21:23,750
Lijuan once told me

353
00:21:23,830 --> 00:21:24,680
her children

354
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:26,270
both loved this song.

355
00:21:26,300 --> 00:21:26,440
♪ Hiding quietly in the corner still ♪

356
00:21:26,440 --> 00:21:27,400
Both?

357
00:21:27,640 --> 00:21:28,160
Yes.

358
00:21:28,350 --> 00:21:29,640
Besides Tong,

359
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:31,000
she also had a daughter, Yang Yan.

360
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:31,060
When Yang Yan was just learning to walk,

361
00:21:31,060 --> 00:21:32,350
♪ The cat hides from me, and
I hide from the cat ♪

362
00:21:32,350 --> 00:21:33,680
she liked listening to this song

363
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:35,940
and playing hide-and-seek with Lijuan.

364
00:21:35,980 --> 00:21:38,300
♪ We're playing hide and seek like that ♪

365
00:21:38,300 --> 00:21:39,970
Please play it again.

366
00:21:40,350 --> 00:21:41,000
Okay.

367
00:21:41,690 --> 00:21:44,720
[Hide and Seek]

368
00:21:51,110 --> 00:21:52,400
Okay. Thank you.

369
00:21:59,890 --> 00:22:01,410
♪ Inside the closet ♪

370
00:22:03,070 --> 00:22:07,380
♪ A cat sits under the window sill ♪

371
00:22:08,170 --> 00:22:12,580
♪ Hiding quietly in the corner still ♪

372
00:22:12,580 --> 00:22:13,420
Both children who died by accident

373
00:22:13,420 --> 00:22:15,440
♪ The cat hides from me, and
I hide from the cat ♪

374
00:22:15,440 --> 00:22:16,880
liked this song.

375
00:22:16,920 --> 00:22:18,490
Yang Youmo died listening to this song.

376
00:22:18,490 --> 00:22:18,640
♪ We're playing hide and seek like that ♪

377
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:20,100
And he was scared to death.

378
00:22:21,070 --> 00:22:22,960
It sounds a bit creepy.

379
00:22:23,570 --> 00:22:25,030
♪ Inside the closet, quiet and low ♪

380
00:22:25,030 --> 00:22:26,690
It's like someone's playing

381
00:22:27,020 --> 00:22:28,710
hide-and-seek with us behind all this.

382
00:22:28,710 --> 00:22:33,290
♪ Hidden where can't be found ♪

383
00:22:33,840 --> 00:22:36,860
♪ You come to seek, I go to hide ♪

384
00:22:36,860 --> 00:22:39,080
[154 km/h]

385
00:22:39,080 --> 00:22:39,460
♪ You'll never find me ♪

386
00:22:39,460 --> 00:22:41,110
[Illegal dumping, remote and filthy]

387
00:22:41,140 --> 00:22:42,170
[Zhao Qian]

388
00:22:42,300 --> 00:22:44,240
[Yang Youmo's house:
Sunshine Waterbank Community]

389
00:22:44,240 --> 00:22:47,450
♪ Let's play hide-and-seek ♪

390
00:22:47,450 --> 00:22:49,170
[Hide and Seek]

391
00:22:49,350 --> 00:22:53,880
♪ You come to seek, I go to hide ♪

392
00:22:54,420 --> 00:22:59,030
♪ I've found a hiding place ♪

393
00:22:59,600 --> 00:22:59,740
[Mom's Diary]

394
00:22:59,740 --> 00:23:02,810
♪ So quiet here, not a trace ♪

395
00:23:09,350 --> 00:23:12,670
[Nanying District Sub-Bureau
Xinggang City Public Security Bureau]

396
00:23:16,070 --> 00:23:17,010
Morning, Captain Zheng.

397
00:23:17,010 --> 00:23:18,670
-Morning.
-Dajun's not here?

398
00:23:25,050 --> 00:23:25,980
What do you mean?

399
00:23:32,700 --> 00:23:34,850
[Breakfast for Uncle]

400
00:23:36,720 --> 00:23:37,200
Morning.

401
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:38,000
Morning, Jun.

402
00:23:38,000 --> 00:23:39,070
Morning.

403
00:23:40,440 --> 00:23:40,960
Dajun,

404
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:43,640
how's the drug source investigation going?

405
00:23:43,640 --> 00:23:44,500
Captain Zheng,

406
00:23:45,030 --> 00:23:46,000
please give me a break.

407
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:47,750
There are so many hospitals...

408
00:23:47,750 --> 00:23:49,590
I've been cutting you slack for days.

409
00:23:49,590 --> 00:23:51,130
Or you want Director Zhang
to give you a break?

410
00:23:51,130 --> 00:23:52,310
That's not necessary.

411
00:23:52,310 --> 00:23:54,070
Hospitals and clinics

412
00:23:54,240 --> 00:23:56,030
have complete purchase and prescription

413
00:23:56,030 --> 00:23:57,070
records.

414
00:23:57,070 --> 00:23:58,920
No missing drug reports either.

415
00:23:59,200 --> 00:24:01,240
Next, I'm going to
look into the black market—

416
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:02,310
track down sources of

417
00:24:02,310 --> 00:24:03,510
adrenaline and anesthetics.

418
00:24:03,510 --> 00:24:04,750
I was just about to say that.

419
00:24:04,750 --> 00:24:05,960
We can't just check the obvious routes—

420
00:24:05,960 --> 00:24:07,400
the shady ones matter even more.

421
00:24:07,400 --> 00:24:09,000
How about this? Let's split up.

422
00:24:09,000 --> 00:24:10,270
You discuss with them

423
00:24:10,270 --> 00:24:11,680
to investigate the black market.

424
00:24:11,680 --> 00:24:13,310
Keran, you, me,

425
00:24:14,200 --> 00:24:15,000
and Advisor Zhong

426
00:24:15,000 --> 00:24:15,920
will go to

427
00:24:16,640 --> 00:24:18,640
Lyuyun Group and see what we can get.

428
00:24:28,960 --> 00:24:30,960
Master, Zhao Qian's back at Lyuyun.

429
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:46,720
Good tea.

430
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:51,510
Is it?

431
00:24:52,270 --> 00:24:53,070
What's the difference

432
00:24:53,070 --> 00:24:54,110
between this and the 50 yuan tea

433
00:24:54,110 --> 00:24:55,040
from our office?

434
00:24:56,310 --> 00:24:58,110
You can take some with you later,

435
00:24:58,200 --> 00:24:59,660
since it suits your taste.

436
00:25:00,310 --> 00:25:01,240
I appreciate it.

437
00:25:01,440 --> 00:25:02,830
But I'm afraid if I accept it,

438
00:25:02,830 --> 00:25:04,490
I might cross the legal limit.

439
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:09,310
Mr. Zhong,

440
00:25:10,480 --> 00:25:13,610
aren't you the divorce lawyer
who knows women very well?

441
00:25:13,750 --> 00:25:15,160
So you're a cop too?

442
00:25:17,160 --> 00:25:19,270
I am a divorce lawyer.

443
00:25:20,590 --> 00:25:22,880
But thanks to Captain Zheng's invitation,

444
00:25:22,880 --> 00:25:24,810
I'm now acting as a special advisor

445
00:25:24,960 --> 00:25:26,220
for the criminal team.

446
00:25:26,550 --> 00:25:27,750
Here's my card.

447
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:30,790
And yes, I know women very well.

448
00:25:31,110 --> 00:25:32,790
If your friends need anything,

449
00:25:32,790 --> 00:25:34,000
they can come to me anytime.

450
00:25:34,000 --> 00:25:34,640
Mention my name—

451
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:35,770
there's a discount.

452
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:37,920
Interesting.

453
00:25:40,640 --> 00:25:41,310
Ms. Zhao,

454
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:43,850
I have something interesting too.

455
00:25:45,350 --> 00:25:46,960
The case of you and Yang Youmo

456
00:25:47,510 --> 00:25:49,270
involves two kinds of drugs.

457
00:25:49,350 --> 00:25:50,350
One of them

458
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:52,890
is a Class I controlled substance.

459
00:25:53,070 --> 00:25:55,110
Ordinary people can't get it easily.

460
00:25:55,110 --> 00:25:57,680
We're tracking the source of both drugs.

461
00:25:57,680 --> 00:25:59,680
And it just so happens—

462
00:25:59,680 --> 00:26:02,480
they're both flagship products
of your Lyuyun Group.

463
00:26:02,480 --> 00:26:03,880
Isn't that interesting?

464
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:06,200
You mean

465
00:26:06,550 --> 00:26:09,270
the murderer deliberately used our drugs

466
00:26:09,680 --> 00:26:10,550
just to

467
00:26:10,720 --> 00:26:12,110
smear Lyuyun's name?

468
00:26:14,310 --> 00:26:15,550
Did I say that?

469
00:26:16,030 --> 00:26:17,160
Ms. Zhao, you're reminding us

470
00:26:17,160 --> 00:26:19,510
there's another investigative angle.

471
00:26:20,590 --> 00:26:21,200
Here's the thing,

472
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:22,480
we'd like to see

473
00:26:22,640 --> 00:26:24,920
your production and distribution

474
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:27,270
records for adrenaline and anesthetics

475
00:26:27,790 --> 00:26:29,190
from the past six months.

476
00:26:29,440 --> 00:26:30,270
Any problem?

477
00:26:32,640 --> 00:26:34,570
Instead of catching the murderer,

478
00:26:34,590 --> 00:26:36,390
now you're coming after Lyuyun.

479
00:26:36,720 --> 00:26:38,250
I don't think this is right.

480
00:26:40,790 --> 00:26:41,510
Ms. Zhao,

481
00:26:42,310 --> 00:26:43,590
this is for

482
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:45,590
your own safety.

483
00:26:46,550 --> 00:26:47,810
Without identifying

484
00:26:47,960 --> 00:26:49,480
the drug source,

485
00:26:49,590 --> 00:26:51,190
we can't catch the murderer.

486
00:26:51,830 --> 00:26:53,510
So you came to Lyuyun

487
00:26:53,830 --> 00:26:55,510
to find the drug source?

488
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:58,680
Fine.

489
00:26:58,960 --> 00:27:01,200
We'll suspend all operations for one day

490
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:03,730
to fully cooperate
with your investigation.

491
00:27:04,750 --> 00:27:06,000
If that's the case,

492
00:27:06,030 --> 00:27:07,070
we appreciate it.

493
00:27:07,070 --> 00:27:08,670
-Thank you.
-Thank you, Ms. Zhao.

494
00:27:08,670 --> 00:27:09,640
Thank you.

495
00:27:09,880 --> 00:27:10,880
Mr. Zhong,

496
00:27:11,750 --> 00:27:13,070
this is not fun.

497
00:27:14,960 --> 00:27:15,480
Ms. Zhao, it's not an easy job.

498
00:27:15,480 --> 00:27:16,930
[Advisor ID]

499
00:27:17,750 --> 00:27:18,880
Please understand.

500
00:27:21,310 --> 00:27:22,960
Okay, I understand.

501
00:27:23,720 --> 00:27:25,450
Then I'll make an announcement

502
00:27:26,580 --> 00:27:29,440
to have Lyuyun,
this massive tax-paying machine,

503
00:27:29,640 --> 00:27:30,750
shut down.

504
00:27:32,310 --> 00:27:33,350
Let me make a call.

505
00:27:33,590 --> 00:27:34,400
Wait a moment.

506
00:27:50,640 --> 00:27:51,400
Shut down?

507
00:27:53,160 --> 00:27:54,550
Who's she calling now?

508
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:56,960
Who she calls doesn't matter.

509
00:27:56,960 --> 00:27:57,960
What matters is—

510
00:27:58,070 --> 00:28:00,240
who your direct superior is.

511
00:28:02,920 --> 00:28:04,440
What's so funny, Master?

512
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:06,240
Nothing. Stand straight later.

513
00:28:06,480 --> 00:28:07,480
That softie in disguise

514
00:28:07,480 --> 00:28:08,480
will be here soon.

515
00:28:09,350 --> 00:28:11,610
Who are you calling a softie in disguise?

516
00:28:11,830 --> 00:28:12,720
Stand still.

517
00:28:15,480 --> 00:28:17,110
Don't you know the rules?

518
00:28:18,400 --> 00:28:21,210
You think you can investigate
Lyuyun Group as you like?

519
00:28:21,210 --> 00:28:23,480
Disrupting Lyuyun's operations

520
00:28:23,550 --> 00:28:24,680
is disrupting

521
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:26,350
Xinggang's economic growth.

522
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:27,370
Understand?

523
00:28:29,640 --> 00:28:31,050
As soon as I got the call,

524
00:28:31,110 --> 00:28:32,110
I rushed over—

525
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:35,130
afraid you'd make an even bigger mess.

526
00:28:37,350 --> 00:28:38,920
Thankfully, Lyuyun and Ms. Zhao

527
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:40,350
didn't take it to heart.

528
00:28:41,480 --> 00:28:42,720
Right, Ms. Zhao?

529
00:28:43,550 --> 00:28:44,350
Sure.

530
00:28:44,830 --> 00:28:46,400
So what exactly are you investigating?

531
00:28:46,400 --> 00:28:49,640
The source of adrenaline
and anesthetic drugs.

532
00:28:49,920 --> 00:28:52,160
You should've spoken to Ms. Zhao nicely.

533
00:28:52,160 --> 00:28:54,160
If your investigation is rational,

534
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:56,480
would she make it hard for you?

535
00:28:56,640 --> 00:28:58,640
Why cause such a misunderstanding?

536
00:28:59,110 --> 00:29:00,790
Alright, I'll supervise you here.

537
00:29:00,790 --> 00:29:03,400
Just finish the investigation
and leave with me.

538
00:29:03,400 --> 00:29:05,130
Don't make more troubles here.

539
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:05,750
Understood.

540
00:29:05,750 --> 00:29:06,480
Understood.

541
00:29:10,270 --> 00:29:10,920
Ms. Zhao,

542
00:29:11,590 --> 00:29:12,720
good tea, by the way.

543
00:29:24,110 --> 00:29:26,070
You heard what Director Zhang said.

544
00:29:26,070 --> 00:29:29,070
Then cooperate with
Captain Zheng's investigation.

545
00:29:29,440 --> 00:29:30,070
Yes.

546
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:31,750
This way, please.

547
00:29:43,350 --> 00:29:44,200
Ms. Zhao,

548
00:29:46,030 --> 00:29:48,690
didn't Yang Youmo's painting
used to hang here?

549
00:29:50,070 --> 00:29:51,330
Why did you take it off?

550
00:29:52,880 --> 00:29:54,810
I didn't want to be reminded of him.

551
00:29:59,060 --> 00:30:00,390
Reminded?

552
00:30:00,790 --> 00:30:02,510
Even if a regular friend died,

553
00:30:03,110 --> 00:30:04,440
I would be sad.

554
00:30:04,440 --> 00:30:06,160
When Qian Cheng died...

555
00:30:06,510 --> 00:30:07,110
Qian.

556
00:30:07,110 --> 00:30:08,070
Behave yourself.

557
00:30:08,070 --> 00:30:09,350
Is it because of that artist?

558
00:30:09,350 --> 00:30:10,110
You're drunk.

559
00:30:10,110 --> 00:30:11,970
Just you wait to go to hell with me.

560
00:30:13,270 --> 00:30:14,350
Are you sad?

561
00:30:16,030 --> 00:30:17,880
Qian Cheng's wife Fang Qinchun

562
00:30:18,640 --> 00:30:19,960
mentioned you a lot.

563
00:30:19,990 --> 00:30:21,220
She said you often...

564
00:30:21,270 --> 00:30:21,960
I know there's been

565
00:30:21,960 --> 00:30:23,880
a lot of gossip about me lately.

566
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:29,920
You know

567
00:30:31,000 --> 00:30:34,240
